<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_123> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_123" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_90> ;
    del:text "The Committee on Budgetary Control adopted with great unanimity a number of amendments that would have improved the transparency and the auditing of the facility. Most of them were not taken on board because the rapporteurs wanted to have a swift negotiation with the Council. I can understand that, but the challenge is still there to strengthen the auditing in Moldova and to make sure that taxpayers' money is used in the best possible way. I am sure that we will have many opportunities to come back to that debate on strengthening the national auditing system in Moldova." ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:15:50"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_124> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_124" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_91> ;
    del:text """In Chi脠聶in脛聝u my impression was 芒聙聯 and I felt 芒聙聯 a profound sense of optimism surrounding the transformative potential of a EUR脗聽1.9脗聽billion facility, because it offers much more than just financial assistance: it brings hope for a brighter future.
The facility will significantly improve the country's infrastructure. Thanks to our support as a European Union, Moldova can finally reduce its dependence on Russia.
But this brings me to a critical point. With more and more malign interference and an intentionally orchestrated energy crisis, the Kremlin is trying to destabilise Moldova's democracy and foster discontent ahead of the upcoming parliamentary elections in autumn.
Moldova embodies Europe's core values, showing unwavering solidarity with Ukrainian refugees, demonstrating remarkable resilience in the face of Russia's blackmail, and displaying immense courage in aligning the country's future with a united Europe. President Maia Sandu has done tremendously in addressing the impact of the war on Moldova's doorstep, while bringing the country closer to the European Union.
Our message to the people of Moldova is and remains: we hear you, we see you, and we will stand by you.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:17:13"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_125> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_125" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_92> ;
    del:text """Cele 1,9 miliarde de euro nu sunt doar un cec de solidaritate, ci un angajament ferm pentru modernizare, stabilitate 脠聶i integrare european脛聝.脗聽Aceste fonduri trebuie s脛聝 produc脛聝 rezultate vizibile pentru cet脛聝脠聸eni.
Am propus amendamente esen脠聸iale care au fost adoptate 脠聶i care vor contribui direct la succesul acestui plan 脠聶i le mul脠聸umesc raportorilor:
- sprijinirea zonelor rurale 脠聶i a politicilor pentru copii, fonduri europene care au s脛聝 ajung脛聝 acolo unde este cea mai mare nevoie,
- implicarea diasporei 脙庐n implementarea m脛聝surilor 芒聙聯 milioane de moldoveni tr脛聝iesc 脠聶i muncesc 脙庐n alte state europene 脠聶i vor juca astfel un rol esen脠聸ial 脙庐n dezvoltarea 脠聸脛聝rii,
- investi脠聸ii strategice 脙庐n interconect脛聝ri cu Rom脙垄nia, mai ales pe zona de energie.
Mai mult, pentru utilizarea eficient脛聝 a acestor fonduri am propus 脠聶i se va deschide chiar acum, s-a aprobat, un birou al Parlamentului European la Chi脠聶in脛聝u, o ini脠聸iativ脛聝 pe care am avut-o 脙庐n calitate de vicepre脠聶edinte al Parlamentului European, responsabil de rela脠聸ia cu Republica Moldova.
Iat脛聝 c脛聝 Republica Moldova are u脠聶a deschis脛聝 脙庐n Europa. Europa sprijin脛聝 Republica Moldova. Republica Moldova are o oportunitate istoric脛聝 pe care nu o poate rata.
Ave脠聸i tot sprijinul din partea Parlamentului European.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:19:03"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_126> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_126" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_93> ;
    del:text """De discussie ging echter niet over deze kwesties, maar voortdurend over Oekra脙炉ne, waarbij Moldavi脙芦 zelfs als frontlinie werd aangeduid. Daar kunnen ze zelf toch ook niet blij mee zijn.
Er is al forse financi脙芦le steun gekoppeld aan het toetredingsproces, maar er is nog meer hulp nodig: twee miljard aan leningen en giften. De Europese Commissie heeft tegen de regels in geen risico芒聙聭inschatting gemaakt. De wensen van de Commissie begrotingscontrole, waaronder een onafhankelijke rekenkamer en transparantie inzake de bestedingen, werden afgewezen. Het gaat om heel veel geld, meer dan 10脗聽% van het bnp, dus kan een land dat 脙录berhaupt verwerken?
Ik heb tegengestemd. Niet alleen vanwege het ontbreken van een analyse vooraf, het ontbreken van controle tijdens het proces en achteraf en het ontbreken van een overzicht van wie uiteindelijk het geld krijgt, maar omdat ik vind dat je voortgang in het toetredingsproces niet kunt kopen. Je onderschat de menselijke factor als je denkt met subsidies corruptie te bestrijden of het gevangeniswezen humaner te maken of de 45脗聽% tegenstemmers in Moldavi脙芦 ook enthousiast te maken voor de Unie. Straks zijn op papier alle maatregelen doorgevoerd, maar is er praktisch niets veranderd, behalve dan dat het land lid is.
Samenlevingen kunnen groeien naar een hoger niveau, maar dat gaat niet sneller als je dat aan de Europese Unie uitbesteedt. Ook niet voor twee miljard.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:20:31"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_127> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_127" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_94> ;
    del:text """Solu脠聸ia la problemele de securitate, economice, sociale 脠聶i politice din Republica Moldova ar fi unirea celor dou脛聝 state. Pl脛聝cile tectonice ale istoriei se mi脠聶c脛聝 脙庐n acest moment 芒聙聯 cu sprijinul Uniunii Europene, visul rom脙垄nilor de o parte 脠聶i de alta a Prutului s-ar putea 脙庐ndeplini.
脠聵tim foarte bine 脙庐ns脛聝 c脛聝 stilul Bruxelles-ului 脠聶i al Strasbourg-ului este trasul de timp, 脙庐n speran脠聸a c脛聝 problemele se vor rezolva de la sine. F脛聝r脛聝 sus脠聸inere adecvat脛聝, f脛聝r脛聝 o diversificare a op脠聸iunilor politice pro-europene 脠聶i pro-rom脙垄ne脠聶ti de la Chi脠聶in脛聝u, pot exista surprize nepl脛聝cute la alegerile parlamentare. Inclusiv unioni脠聶tii trebuie sprijini脠聸i.
Revenind la mecanismul pe care vre脠聸i s脛聝-l institui脠聸i, AUR consider脛聝 c脛聝 orice sprijin pentru fra脠聸ii basarabeni este de bun augur. Dar vreau s脛聝 fac trei observa脠聸ii:
- 脙庐n primul r脙垄nd, moldovenii vor vedea c脛聝 din acea sum脛聝 total脛聝 de 1,9 miliarde de euro, doar 520 de milioane de euro sunt granturi, restul fiind 脙庐mprumuturi condi脠聸ionate. Raportul dintre banii nerambursabili 脠聶i credite trebuia s脛聝 fie invers;
- 脙庐n al doilea r脙垄nd, reformele cerute 脙庐n Republica Moldova vor fi 脙庐ntoarse de pro-ru脠聶i 脙庐mpotriva actualei administra脠聸ii 脠聶i folosite 脙庐n alegerile parlamentare. A se vedea 脠聶i blocajul PNRR din Rom脙垄nia, condi脠聸ionat tot de reforme care nu s-au realizat. Cere脠聸i mai mult dec脙垄t poate duce un guvern de la Chi脠聶in脛聝u aflat sub asediu necontenit;
- 脠聶i nu 脙庐n ultimul r脙垄nd, dac脛聝 vre脠聸i s脛聝 rezolva脠聸i problema energetic脛聝 a Republicii Moldova, trebuie revizuit脛聝 situa脠聸ia pie脠聸ei unice europene. Rom脙垄nia, care este autosuficient脛聝 pe gaze 脠聶i electricitate, a ajuns s脛聝 pl脛聝teasc脛聝 cele mai mari facturi din Uniunea European脛聝. Acest lucru este relevant pentru c脛聝 Republica Moldova a sc脛聝pat de dependen脠聸a de Rusia, import脙垄nd toate gazele 脠聶i tot curentul din Rom脙垄nia. Noi producem 脠聶i import脛聝m 脙庐n acest moment pentru dou脛聝 state.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:22:38"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_128> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_128" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_95> ;
    del:text """La referendumul privind aderarea Republicii Moldova la Uniunea European脛聝, Rusia a risipit peste 100 de milioane de euro 脙庐n bani murdari, 脙庐ncerc脙垄nd s脛聝 influen脠聸eze rezultatul. 脙聨ns脛聝 Chi脠聶in脛聝ul a rezistat 脙庐ntr-un mod absolut exemplar, iar Moldova este ast脛聝zi un adev脛聝rat model pentru statele deja membre ale Uniunii 脙庐n ceea ce prive脠聶te combaterea amenin脠聸脛聝rilor hibride. Un stat care din 1992 rezist脛聝 cu Armata a 14-a a Rusiei pe teritoriul s脛聝u, care a s脛聝rit 脙庐n ajutorul Ucrainei odat脛聝 cu invazia rus脛聝 脠聶i care nu se abate nicio secund脛聝 de la viitorul european, merit脛聝 tot sprijinul nostru.
Iar pentru Vladimir Putin mesajul este unul foarte clar: Europa 脠聶tie s脛聝 se mobilizeze 脠聶i s脛聝 sprijine concret un stat prieten 脠聶i candidat la aderare. Putin a 脙庐ncercat s脛聝 p脛聝c脛聝leasc脛聝 o 脠聸ar脛聝 cu 100 de milioane pentru propagand脛聝. Noi r脛聝spundem cu 2 miliarde, cu aproape 2 miliarde pentru dezvoltare. Da, domnule Putin, Uniunea exist脛聝 脠聶i nu pleac脛聝 nic脛聝ieri.
Oric脙垄t s-ar schimba direc脠聸ia din care bate v脙垄ntul geopolitic, un lucru este confirmat ast脛聝zi din nou: Europa nu-脠聶i va abandona alia脠聸ii 脠聶i prietenii. Avem capacitatea 脠聶i avem determinarea de a p脛聝stra Europa un continent al p脛聝cii 脠聶i bun脛聝st脛聝rii pentru oameni. M脙垄ine, la votul pentru facilitatea de cre脠聶tere, vom face un pas ferm 脙庐n aceast脛聝 direc脠聸ie. 脙聨n cazul Moldovei vom mai face pa脠聶i la negocierea viitorului buget multianual, 脙庐n care ea 脠聶i celelalte state candidate trebuie s脛聝 primeasc脛聝 fonduri de preaderare.
Nimic nu ne va abate de la acest drum, la fel cum Moldova nu a ezitat niciodat脛聝 s脛聝 probeze cu fapte aspira脠聸ia european脛聝.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:24:44"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_129> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_129" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_96> ;
    del:text """Now we have to deliver. And we do. With this EUR脗聽1.9脗聽billion Reform and Growth Facility for Moldova, we support Moldova's path to EU accession. We help to mitigate the challenges that arise from the Russian war of aggression against Ukraine. We help to strengthen Moldova's administration, civil society and judicial system. And we help Moldova to gain independency in their energy supply.脗聽And on this, the Moldovan Government was quite clear: Moldova wants to build up renewables; Moldova wants to increase energy efficiency; Moldova wants to work on building renovation.
In this way, we support the Moldovan Government and we are proud to help prepare Moldova to become a member of the European Union.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:26:50"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_13> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_13" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_7> ;
    del:text """On February 24, the official mission of this Parliament's delegation for relations with Palestine, of which I am the Chair, was supposed to take place. Instead, myself, Rima Hassan, MEP, and two officials of this Parliament were detained by the Israeli authorities and subsequently deported.
While detained by the Israeli authorities, our electronic devices held by Members and staff of the delegation were confiscated for over 90 minutes. Our passports, including an Irish diplomatic passport, were confiscated and were not returned to us until we arrived back in Brussels.
This all took place on the same day that the EU-Israel Association Council was taking place, and EU leaders were committing themselves to continue business as usual with Israel, while the Israeli authorities were not allowing us, as elected officials, to do our jobs.
So I ask you, Madam President, that you address this matter urgently.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T17:14:07"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_130> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_130" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_97> ;
    del:text """Putin is not afraid that NATO would want to attack by coming close to Russia's borders. He has moved his troops from the NATO borders into Ukraine. And Putin is not concerned about the safety of the Russian-speaking minority in Moldova. He's bombing Russian speakers in Ukraine.
But Putin is afraid of democracy and successful states near the Russian borders. He wants their neighbours to be poor and miserable. Now, when the US is leaving Moldova, Russia still wants to suppress Moldova. Moldova needs us now more than ever. We must stand up and take responsibility for this facility and more broadly.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:28:05"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_131> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_131" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_98> ;
    del:text """2脗聽Milliarden脗聽Euro wollen Sie jetzt nach Moldawien schicken, als Vorschuss f脙录r die EU芒聙聭Mitgliedschaft. Wir lehnen diese Verschwendung ab, weil der gr脙露脙聼te Teil dieses Geldes in den Taschen von korrupten Politikern und Oligarchen verschwinden wird. Im Korruptionsindex von Transparency International steht Moldau auf den hinteren Pl脙陇tzen. Weil wir die Interessen der Steuerzahler in Deutschland und Frankreich und anderen Mitgliedstaaten verteidigen m脙录ssen, lehnen wir die 2脗聽Milliarden脗聽Euro f脙录r Moldawien ab, denn f脙录r die Spendierfreudigkeit in diesem Haus m脙录ssen wir Deutschen horrende Steuern zahlen.
Selbst die Rente wird in Deutschland versteuert. 脙聹ber 7脗聽Millionen Rentner in Deutschland haben weniger als 1脗聽000脗聽Euro im Monat nach vielen Jahrzehnten harter Arbeit. Insgesamt zahlen die Deutschen fast 1脗聽000脗聽Milliarden Euro Steuern im Jahr, und trotzdem fehlt es an allen Ecken und Enden. Br脙录cken und Stra脙聼en verfallen, Schulen und Universit脙陇ten sind marode, Krankenh脙陇user m脙录ssen schlie脙聼en. Der desolate Zustand Deutschlands l脙陇sst sich nur noch mit gigantischen Schulden verschleiern. Deshalb m脙录ssen wir die Verschwendung beenden, und wir werden dieser EU den Geldhahn abdrehen.
Margaret Thatcher hat mal gesagt: Das Problem der Sozialisten ist, dass ihnen irgendwann das Geld fremder Leute ausgeht. So ist es auch hier. Wenn Deutschland nicht mehr zahlt, dann ist die Party vorbei. Europa kann nur eine Zukunft haben, wenn europ脙陇ische Politiker die Interessen ihrer W脙陇hler an erste Stelle setzen, und genau das werden wir tun. Sp脙陇testens nach der n脙陇chsten Bundestagswahl gilt: Schluss mit der Gro脙聼z脙录gigkeit auf Deutschlands Nacken, Schluss mit den unsinnigen Geldgeschenken an alle Welt.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:29:29"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_132> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_132" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_99> ;
    del:text """Ovaj fond, vrijedan gotovo 1,9 milijardi eura, potaknut 脛聡e Moldovu na provedbu nu脜戮nih reformi, ja脛聧anje institucija i ubrzanje integracije u europske, gospodarske i politi脛聧ke tokove kroz usko povezivanje investicija s reformama, sli脛聧no kao i za plan rasta za takozvani zapadni Balkan.
Pove脛聡ano pretfinanciranje i dodatna bespovratna sredstva osigurat 脛聡e ne samo da dr脜戮ava izdr脜戮i trenutne izazove, ve脛聡 i ostvari konkretne pomake na svom europskom putu. Ulaganje u sigurnost, ulaganje u demokraciju i stabilnost na脜隆eg susjedstva ulaganje je u sigurniju i prosperitetniju Europu za sve nas.
脛聦estitam izvjestiteljima Siegfriedu Mure脜聼anu i Svenu Mikseru na njihovom trudu i na uspje脜隆nom zavr脜隆etku pregovora.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:31:43"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_133> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_133" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_100> ;
    del:text """Neste processo, ficou patente que, quando chamado com urg脙陋ncia a pronunciar-se, o Parlamento Europeu est脙隆 apto a responder, fazendo da solidariedade europeia a sua prioridade. E, enquanto codecisor, autoridade or脙搂amental, est脙隆 脙聽 altura daquelas que s脙拢o as suas atribui脙搂脙碌es pelo Tratado 芒聙聰 e continuar脙隆 a estar, sem d脙潞vida, em todos os processos.
O Parlamento fez ainda ajustes importantes neste mecanismo, nomeadamente no aumento da taxa de pr脙漏-financiamento de 7脗聽% para 18脗聽% e na altera脙搂脙拢o da componente 脗芦subs脙颅dio脗禄 de 16脗聽% para 20,5脗聽%. Defendemos tamb脙漏m uma maior capacidade administrativa da Mold脙隆via e, por isso, temos mais financiamento dedicado ao fortalecimento das suas institui脙搂脙碌es.
Por fim, o Parlamento tem ainda uma supervis脙拢o refor脙搂ada, num di脙隆logo entre o Parlamento e a Comiss脙拢o, para rever o progresso na implementa脙搂脙拢o deste mecanismo.
Fica claro o nosso compromisso com o povo moldavo e o nosso empenho no percurso da Mold脙隆via rumo 脙聽 ades脙拢o 脙聽 Uni脙拢o Europeia.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:33:05"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_134> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_134" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_101> ;
    del:text """Si ces choix se faisaient par r脙漏f脙漏rendum, les contribuables d芒聙聶Europe diraient non 脙聽 vos d脙漏lires. Pourquoi spolier les citoyens europ脙漏ens 脙聽 travers des subventions non remboursables et des pr脙陋ts 脙聽 un pays dont le PIB par habitant reste 脙聽 29脗聽% de la moyenne des pays de l芒聙聶Union? Croyez-vous r脙漏ellement que la Moldavie pourra rembourser le volet compos脙漏 de pr脙陋ts? C芒聙聶est un v脙漏ritable gaspillage des ressources europ脙漏ennes.
Nous nous y opposerons et nous nous opposerons aussi 脙聽 la candidature de la Moldavie 脙聽 l芒聙聶Union europ脙漏enne, tout comme 脙聽 l芒聙聶脙漏largissement aux Balkans et 脙聽 l芒聙聶Ukraine, qui ne seraient en plus pas contributeurs nets au budget de l芒聙聶Union. 脙聙 la catastrophe financi脙篓re s芒聙聶ajouterait aussi une catastrophe agricole.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:34:47"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_135> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_135" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_102> ;
    del:text "Polska wspiera Mo脜聜dawi脛聶 od momentu uzyskania przez ni脛聟 niepodleg脜聜o脜聸ci. Mam osobist脛聟 satysfakcj脛聶, 脜录e jako minister spraw wewn脛聶trznych mog脜聜em uczestniczy脛聡 w tej pomocy. W 2023 r. w obliczu prorosyjskich pr脙鲁b destabilizacji, prorosyjskich boj脙鲁wek na ulicach Kiszyniowa przekazali脜聸my mo脜聜dawskiemu MSW bardzo du脜录脛聟 ilo脜聸脛聡 sprz脛聶tu policyjnego, w tym bro脜聞 i amunicj脛聶, aby Mo脜聜dawia by脜聜a samowystarczalna w zakresie zapewnienia porz脛聟dku publicznego. Dajmy szans脛聶 Mo脜聜dawii uciec przed dyktatur脛聟 Putina. Jestem przekonany, 脜录e wsparcie finansowe, nad kt脙鲁rym jutro b脛聶dziemy g脜聜osowa脛聡, dobrze si脛聶 do tego przyczyni." ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:36:03"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_136> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_136" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_103> ;
    del:text """脙聨ns脛聝, doamn脛聝 comisar脛聝, vreau s脛聝 脠聶ti脠聸i, Republica Moldova este singurul stat aflat 脙庐n imediata vecin脛聝tate a Uniunii Europene, unde peste jum脛聝tate din cet脛聝脠聸enii s脛聝i sunt deja cet脛聝脠聸eni ai Uniunii Europene. Deci avem toat脛聝 legitimitatea pentru a ne preocupa 脙庐n mod constant de viitorul Republicii Moldova, s-o sprijinim 脙庐n fa脠聸a provoc脛聝rilor care vin dinspre Kremlin 脙庐n mod constant.
De asemenea, este foarte bine c脛聝 acorda脠聸i o aten脠聸ie sporit脛聝 regiunii ocupate 脙庐n mod ilegal de c脛聝tre armata Federa脠聸iei Ruse de mai bine de 30 de ani. Este important ca Republica Moldova s脛聝 tr脛聝iasc脛聝 脙庐n pace 脠聶i s脛聝 beneficieze de suportul Uniunii Europene.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:37:23"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_137> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_137" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_104> ;
    del:text """In the quickly changing world order, we need to start backing words with deeds. And this growth plan shows that we will invest to lift people out of poverty, build solar panels, schools and hospitals. This growth plan shows strong reforms will make Moldova ready to join the EU. And this growth plan shows Europe chose Moldova.
And it tells it tells those that want to join our Union, if you walk the path to Europe, Europe will walk with you. We did this in four months, which for the EU is as fast as travelling at the speed of light. And the Moldovans are not wasting time either. Last week they joined the Single Euro Payments Area.
So let's vote in favour of this growth plan and show the people in Moldova, you'll never walk alone.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:38:43"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_138> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_138" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_105> ;
    del:text """Immerhin wurde uns im Haushaltsausschuss des Parlaments eine Studie pr脙陇sentiert, der zufolge die Aufnahme der drei ehemaligen Sowjetrepubliken Moldau, Georgien und Ukraine die Union an die Grenzen ihrer Belastbarkeit f脙录hren w脙录rde. Ohne einen dramatischen Anstieg der Zahlungsverpflichtungen der Mitgliedstaaten oder drastische K脙录rzungen bei der Gemeinsamen Agrarpolitik oder den Koh脙陇sionsfonds wird sich das nicht machen lassen.
Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, angesichts ohnehin schon wachsender Spaltungstendenzen innerhalb der Union gef脙陇hrden wir mit diesen Erweiterungspl脙陇nen die Zukunft unserer Union. Das sollten wir nicht tun.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:40:04"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_139> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_139" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_106> ;
    del:text """However, Moldova still faces substantial external challenges. The ongoing threats from Russia, including the instability in the region of Transnistria, continue to jeopardise Moldova's sovereignty and European aspirations.
Despite these pressures, Moldova has remained determined, pushing forward with its reforms and advancing EU standards with unwavering resolve. And the growth facility is not just a financial tool, it is a clear message of our united support for Moldova.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:41:49"^^xsd:dateTime .

