<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_145> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_145" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_112> ;
    del:text """脙聨n acela脠聶i timp, Federa脠聸ia Rus脛聝 脠聶i-a 脙庐nchis pia脠聸a pentru produsele din Republica Moldova, Federa脠聸ia Rus脛聝 a 脙庐ntrerupt gazele 脙庐n plin脛聝 iarn脛聝, 脠聶i a exportat r脛聝zboi hibrid.
Este interesat脛聝 Moscova de Republica Moldova? Da, cu siguran脠聸脛聝, pentru c脛聝 pentru Moscova, Republica Moldova are o valoare de 脙庐ntrebuin脠聸are, ca zon脛聝 tampon pe care 脠聶i-o doresc.
Pentru noi, oamenii sunt importan脠聸i 脠聶i 脛聝sta e motivul pentru care vom fi al脛聝turi de cet脛聝脠聸enii din Republica Moldova, indiferent de etnie, de limba pe care o vorbesc 脠聶i de origini. Pute脠聸i s脛聝 conta脠聸i pe noi 脙庐n continuare.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:49:42"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_146> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_146" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_113> ;
    del:text """We must bolster Moldova's resilience now. This is about more than financial aid. It is about resilience, reforms and Moldova's EU path. Strengthening institutions, independent media and electoral integrity must be immediate, not gradual.
The first payout is set at 20脗聽%, but in this critical moment, that's not enough. We should amend the plan and increase it by an additional 5脗聽%. Moving faster and further sends a clear message: Moldova belongs in Europe, free from malign influence.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:51:05"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_147> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_147" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_114> ;
    del:text """Planul de cre脠聶tere al Uniunii Europene este un semnal clar. Republica Moldova trebuie sprijinit脛聝 s脛聝 se decupleze definitiv de influen脠聸ele r脛聝s脛聝ritene. Reforma, modernizarea, distan脠聸area fa脠聸脛聝 de mo脠聶tenirea sovietic脛聝, toate acestea trebuie 脙庐ncurajate cu fermitate.
Am votat pentru un sprijin de 1,9 miliarde de euro pentru Republica Moldova. Nu este doar un ajutor financiar, este o declara脠聸ie politic脛聝 c脛聝 suntem al脛聝turi de fra脠聸ii no脠聶tri de peste Prut.
Uniunea face puterea 脠聶i poate 脙庐ntr-o zi aceast脛聝 reunire politic脛聝, economic脛聝 脠聶i sufleteasc脛聝 va fi des脛聝v脙垄r脠聶it脛聝 sub acela脠聶i tricolor 脙庐n Uniunea European脛聝.
P脙垄n脛聝 atunci, Republica Moldova are nevoie de sprijinul nostru. Acum, aici, concret.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:52:16"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_148> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_148" ;
