<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_175> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_175" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_112> ;
    del:text "Propun, 脙庐n acest sens, introducerea unui pa脠聶aport european pentru radioizotopi medicali, integrat 脙庐n dosarul digital european de s脛聝n脛聝tate. Acest instrument digital ar permite identificarea rapid脛聝 脠聶i discret脛聝 a pacien脠聸ilor trata脠聸i recent cu radioizotopi, simplific脙垄nd controalele de securitate 脠聶i protej脙垄nd totodat脛聝 confiden脠聸ialitatea datelor personale." ;
