<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_190> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_190" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_138> ;
    del:text """But this has not materialised in my country. The price of car insurance continues to rise every year, especially for young drivers, like Patrick O'Reilly from Cornafean in County Cavan: a 19-year-old boy who could insure his 2020 Volkswagen Golf for EUR脗聽1脗聽212 in Belgium, yet is asked to pay a staggering EUR脗聽4脗聽679 in Ireland.
Commissioner, this is nothing short of a rip-off and no amount of prevarication over injury claims or legal costs can excuse it. We need our new Consumer Commissioner, Michael McGrath, to be brave and to seize on this issue, challenge the main players in Europe and make the single market work for European consumers.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T21:53:29"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_191> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_191" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_139> ;
    del:text """O objetivo 脙漏 que possamos garantir que as gera脙搂脙碌es futuras tenham acesso a 脙隆gua para consumo e tamb脙漏m para as v脙隆rias atividades econ脙鲁micas, particularmente a agricultura.
O sul da Europa e, particularmente, Portugal sofrem atualmente uma elevada escassez de 脙隆gua. No nosso caso, as regi脙碌es do Alentejo e do Algarve s脙拢o as mais afetadas.
Portugal apresentou ontem a Estrat脙漏gia Nacional para a Gest脙拢o da 脙聛gua, que tem por nome 脗芦脙聛gua que une脗禄, que prev脙陋 resolver a escassez de 脙隆gua, quer para consumo humano quer para outras utiliza脙搂脙碌es. Est脙隆 previsto um investimento de mais de 5脗聽mil脗聽milh脙碌es de euros.脗聽Por isso, espero que a Uni脙拢o Europeia seja solid脙隆ria, que assuma as suas responsabilidades e que ajude os Estados-Membros.
脙聛gua 脙漏 vida nos territ脙鲁rios, 脙隆gua 脙漏 coes脙拢o social, 脙隆gua 脙漏 economia, 脙隆gua 脙漏 seguran脙搂a. Sim, falo da 脙隆gua e da 脙隆gua que nos une na Uni脙拢o Europeia.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T21:54:50"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_192> a del:Contribution ;
    del:identifier "contribution_192" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_140> ;
    del:text """Derri脙篓re ces financements se cache un v脙漏ritable r脙漏seau militant qui, avec l芒聙聶argent des contribuables, encourage l芒聙聶immigration massive, bloque les expulsions et combat les 脙聣tats qui d脙漏fendent leur souverainet脙漏. Bruxelles finance ceux qui sabotent nos d脙漏mocraties, r脙漏pandent le poison wokiste ou imposent une 脙漏cologie punitive aux Europ脙漏ens, pendant que nos industries s芒聙聶effondrent et que nos peuples s芒聙聶appauvrissent.
Il est temps de mettre fin 脙聽 cette propagande financ脙漏e par l芒聙聶Union europ脙漏enne. L芒聙聶argent des Europ脙漏ens doit servir 脙聽 l芒聙聶int脙漏r脙陋t des Europ脙漏ens, pas aux id脙漏ologies bruxelloises et 脙聽 ses lobbys.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T21:56:15"^^xsd:dateTime .

